{"id": 3031, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在线上和线下的交友标准都有啥区别？", "description": "在网上和在现实中，你都是怎么跟其他人发展出友谊的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 4875, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191017233234nI0ShkroZ52uwXgy.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5967, "title": "你在线上和线下的交友标准都有啥区别？", "content": "你在线上和线下的交友标准都有啥区别？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348431, "content": "线上更看重所谓的“三观一致”，线下反而会放宽一些", "image": "img/option/option/20191017221755dYDoIJqFcBh8bUZC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348432, "content": "线上友谊往往来自爱好特长，线下更多来自熟悉/亲切", "image": "img/option/option/201910172217431MynxibjuNhYVLTQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348433, "content": "在线上喜欢讲话犀利的人，线下却有可能受不了", "image": "img/option/option/20191017222610C4XxqtncNhH7vDyk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348434, "content": "线下朋友在线上一般也熟，但纯线上朋友现实未必认识", "image": "img/option/option/20191017223119wWINTr6lg3c1AK7o.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348435, "content": "线上友谊以社交平台来分类，不同阵地有不同的朋友", "image": "img/option/option/201910172248461j9J64pqAPYlMSZF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348437, "content": "线上交友会预设标准，线下则更像是“遇到了再适应”", "image": "img/option/option/20191017225906DxuKFoJYlyNg5O98.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348439, "content": "比较严肃/隐私的话题，更适合跟线上好友讨论", "image": "img/option/option/20191017230750jEkaRltvfpu30bmA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348440, "content": "现实中能看到动作/态度/神情，表达能力不是首要的", "image": "img/option/option/20191017231332vUM3icxA5ztI6XS4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348441, "content": "我还好，线上线下的交友原则都是一样的", "image": "img/option/option/20191017231612OGgXJQUbzZC1q7it.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348442, "content": "都不是，我有别的答案", "image": "img/option/option/20191017231752zqjCWms36yI457iA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}